Class CoreValidatorParameters

java.lang.Object
se.swedenconnect.opensaml.common.validation.CoreValidatorParameters
public class CoreValidatorParameters extends Object
Core parameter keys used to store and retrieve static and dynamic parameters within a ValidationContext. See also SAML2AssertionValidationParameters.
